          "effect": "The name collector honors the achievement with a new name. The creature gets a +1 status bonus on the same check until their next daily preparations. They become temporarily immune for 1 month.",
          "frequency": "once per day",
          "name": "Name the Worthy",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "traits": [
            {
              "alternate_link": {
